a:17:{s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";s:11:"small_descr";s:162:"AyurSlim has a favorable effect on weight reduction and lipid profiles. It is a researched ayurvedic herbal product, that can be safely used with no side effects.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:175:"AyurSlim hilft bei der Erhaltung gesunden Körpergewicht, reguliert den Fettstoffwechsel. Es ist ein ayurvedisches Arzneimittel, das ohne Nebenwirkungen verwendet werden kann.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:210:"AyurSlim a un effet favorable sur la réduction de poids et la couche adipeuse. C'est un produit ayurvédique sur la base de plantes documentées, qui peut être utilisé sans danger et sans effets secondaires.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:210:"AyurSlim tiene un efecto favorable sobre la reducción de peso y los perfiles de lípidos. Es un producto ayurvédico de hierbas  investigado, que puede ser utilizado de manera segura y sin efectos secundarios.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:186:"AyurSlim ha un effetto favorevole sulla perdita di peso e profilo lipidico.  E' un prodotto erbale ayurvedico ricercato, che può essere usato senza problemi e senza effetti collaterali.";s:10:"full_descr";s:2385:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>AyurSlim reduces the craving for food, thereby reducing the intake of fats and carbohydrates, leads to optimal utilization of nutrients and inhibits fatty acid synthesis, thereby reducing fat accumulation in the body.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>The recommended dosage is 2 capsules twice a day, after meals.<br /><br /> AyurSlim should be taken in conjunction with a reduced calorie diet and half an hour of exercise on a daily basis. <br /><br /> AyurSlim is contraindicated (not advisable) in pregnancy. But it can be taken safely after lochia stops. <br /><br /> AyurSlim is contraindicated in patients with jaundice and renal failure. <br /><br /> In cases, where people are already suffering from problems like diabetes, cardiac problems &amp; high blood pressure, it is preferable to take AyurSlim under medical supervision.</p><p>If you miss a dose of this medicine and you are using it regularly, take it as soon as possible. Do not take 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>The recommended dosage is 2 capsules twice a day, after meals.</p><p><strong>STORAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Store AyurSlim Capsules at room temperature, between 59 and 80 degrees F (15 and 26 degrees C). Store in a tightly closed container. Store away from heat and light. Keep AyurSlim Capsules out of the reach of children and away from pets.</p><p><strong>MORE INFO:</strong></p><p>AyurSlim is an ayurvedic herbal product.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>There are no known warnings or precautions.</p><p>Please, be sure that you are not allergic to the following AyurSlim components:</p><ul><li>Garcinia cambogia (Garcinia, Vrikshamla) limits the synthesis of fatty acids in the muscles and liver. It also arrests lipogenesis (production of fat). </li><li>Commiphora wightii (Indian Bedellium, Guggulu) reduces cholesterol and triglyceride levels.&nbsp;</li><li>Gymnema sylvestre (Meshashringi) abolishes the taste of sugar and neutralizes excess sugar present in the body.</li><li>Terminalia chebula (Chebulic Myrobalan, Haritaki) detoxifies the body and has purgative action.</li><li>Trigonella foenum-graecum (Fenugreek, Medhika) effectively reduces weight.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>AyurSlim is not known to have any side effects if taken as prescribed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:8:"34.87125";s:9:"pack_name";s:5:"packs";s:4:"type";s:4:"caps";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:60;a:6:{i:5013;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5013";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"41.025";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";}i:5014;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5014";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"37.33275";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";}i:5015;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5015";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"36.102";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";}i:5016;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5016";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"35.48663";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";}i:5017;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5017";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"35.1174";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";}i:5018;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5018";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"34.87125";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurslim";}}}}